---
title: Cajun Spiced Roasted Vegetable Stew with Chicken Breast with Rice and Coriander Yoghurt
description: We love Cajun Spiced Roasted Vegetable Stew with Chicken Breast and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
